sentences.sentence: In fact, she added, far too many people are overfeed.
sentences.translation: 事实上，她加上，更多的人喂的过饱。

sentences.sentence: You cannot overfeed a kitten so don't be afraid to give her too much.
sentences.translation: 你再怎么多喂也没关系，所以不要怕给你的猫太多食物。

sentences.sentence: According to Mark Twight, he did not overfeed to make the guys look huge.
sentences.translation: 据马克晨光，他不喂，使球员看起来巨大的。
